sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token Auth
    participant KServe as KServe Controller<br/>Co-manages InferenceService
    participant Istio as Istio Control Plane<br/>Service Mesh Config
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>Auth Policy Engine
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP Bearer

    %% Flow 1: InferenceService Creation & Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>kubectl apply -f isvc.yaml<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    Note over K8sAPI: InferenceService created<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>InferenceService created<br/>K8s Watch API
    K8sAPI->>KServe: Watch Event<br/>InferenceService created

    Note over Controller: Determine deployment mode:<br/>ModelMesh / KServe Serverless / KServe Raw

    %% Serverless Mode Reconciliation
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServingRuntime<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over K8sAPI: ServingRuntime created<br/>(vLLM/TGIS/Caikit/OVMS)

    KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Note over K8sAPI: Knative Service created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Webhook validation request<br/>POST /validate-serving-knative-dev-v1-service<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP mTLS
    Controller-->>K8sAPI: Validation response<br/>Allowed/Denied

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over K8sAPI: Route: {isvc}-{ns}.{domain}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Edge TLS

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Note over K8sAPI: VirtualService for traffic routing

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Note over Istio: mTLS STRICT mode enabled

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Note over Authorino: Authentication policy configured

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Note over Prometheus: Scrape config registered

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Note over K8sAPI: Traffic control rules applied

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshMember<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Note over Istio: Namespace added to mesh

    %% Flow 2: Monitoring Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Ongoing Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Bearer Token
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics<br/>Prometheus format
    end

    %% Flow 3: Serving Runtime Template Deployment
    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Serving Runtime Template Deployment
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List ServingRuntime templates<br/>ConfigMap labeled:<br/>opendatahub.io/dashboard=true
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: vLLM, TGIS, Caikit, OVMS configs
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ServingRuntime<br/>Apply template to namespace
    end

    %% Health Checks
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over K8sAPI,Controller: Health Monitoring (Continuous)
        K8sAPI->>Controller: GET /healthz<br/>8081/TCP HTTP
        Controller-->>K8sAPI: OK
        K8sAPI->>Controller: GET /readyz<br/>8081/TCP HTTP
        Controller-->>K8sAPI: OK
    end
